OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has vowed to "call
OL,8,Ftime on a system that's failing our
OL,9,Fkids" ahead of his expected
OL,10,Fannouncement of an under-16s social
OL,11,Fmedia ban.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister will announce
OL,14,Fsweeping reforms to protect children
OL,15,Fonline at a Downing Street press
OL,16,Fconference on Monday.
OL,26,@oD@_OUqD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FHe promised "bold action" in response
OL,8,Fto calls for change from parents,
OL,9,Fafter the vast majority responding to
OL,10,Fthe Government consultation backed a
OL,11,Fminimum age of 16 before children can
OL,12,Faccess social media platforms.
OL,14,FThe UK is expected to follow
OL,15,FAustralia's example in raising the
OL,16,Fminimum age to 16 for sites including
OL,17,FTikTok, Instagram, Threads, Facebook,
OL,18,FX, YouTube, Snapchat and Reddit.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FBut the ban will go further than
OL,8,FAustralia's by including romantic or
OL,9,Fsexual AI chatbots, and children could
OL,10,Falso be blocked from chatting to
OL,11,Fstrangers on gaming platforms,
OL,12,Faccording to The Sunday Times.
OL,14,FThe newspaper reported that daily
OL,15,Fsocial media use will be limited for
OL,16,Funder-18s in a bid to stop late-night
OL,17,Fscrolling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FThe public consultation on the issue,
OL,8,Fwhich closed on May 26, received about
OL,9,F116,000 responses, making it the
OL,10,Fsecond-largest in history.
OL,12,FOver 83% of parents who responded said
OL,13,Fsocial media risks outweigh the
OL,14,Fbenefits for children ` with 91%
OL,15,Fbacking a minimum age of 16 before
OL,16,Fplatforms can offer their services to
OL,17,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FAlmost two thirds (62%) of children
OL,8,Fwho responded said restricting the
OL,9,Fhigh-risk features would make them
OL,10,Fsafer online.
OL,12,FBut 72% also said they were worried
OL,13,Fabout feeling left out if restrictions
OL,14,Fcame in.
OL,16,FSir Keir said: "How we keep kids safe
OL,17,Fonline is one of the biggest debates
OL,18,Fof our time. As a dad, I know every
OL,19,Fparent wants their child to grow up
OL,20,Fsafe and happy.
OL,26,@xD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,F"This is a choice about whose side
OL,8,Fwe're on: families across the country,
OL,9,For a status quo that isn't working.
OL,11,F"People rightly expect action, and
OL,12,Fthis Government will always stand up
OL,13,Ffor parents and put children first.
OL,15,F"That's why we will call time on a
OL,16,Fsystem that's failing our kids and
OL,17,Ftake bold action to give every child
OL,18,Fthe best possible start in life."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FIt comes after Sir Keir last week
OL,8,Fissued a three-month ultimatum to
OL,9,FApple and Google to make it
OL,10,Ftechnologically impossible for
OL,11,Fchildren to take, share or view nude
OL,12,Fimages on their smartphones.
OL,14,FThe latest move risks prompting a
OL,15,Fbacklash from Donald Trump's pro-tech
OL,16,FUS administration, which warned
OL,17,Fagainst a blanket ban for under-16s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FIn a response to the consultation, the
OL,8,FUS embassy in London said the country
OL,9,Fpreferred "narrowly targeted
OL,10,Frequirements", that "most content
OL,11,Fshould be accessible by default", and
OL,12,Fthat age verification requirements
OL,13,Fcould "impose disproportionate
OL,14,Fcompliance burdens on American
OL,15,Fcompanies".
OL,17,FThe Prime Minister's announcement
OL,18,Fcomes at a difficult time for his
OL,19,Fpremiership, which has been under
OL,20,Fpressure since Labour's drubbing in
OL,21,FMay's local and devolved elections.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@MO]rD@UOUsD@`O]uD@GOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FHis authority was dealt a further blow
OL,8,Flast week by the resignations of the
OL,9,Fdefence secretary and the armed forces
OL,10,Fminister over military funding, and he
OL,11,Fcould face a leadership challenge if
OL,12,FAndy Burnham succeeds in his bid to
OL,13,Freturn to Westminster in this week's
OL,14,FMakerfield by-election.
OL,16,FTory shadow education secretary Laura
OL,17,FTrott said: "It's shameful that it's
OL,18,Ftaken the Prime Minister's job to be
OL,19,Fon the line for the Government to
OL,20,Ffinally U-turn and ban social media
OL,21,Ffor under 16s.
OL,26,@yD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,F"Three times Labour voted against a
OL,8,Fban, failing to stand up to Big Tech
OL,9,Fand protect children from the extreme
OL,10,Fcontent they are exposed to every day.
OL,12,F"As Conservatives we did not give up,
OL,13,FI kept fighting for the brave bereaved
OL,14,Fparents, health professionals, and
OL,15,Fcampaigners who continued to make the
OL,16,Fcase for change. This victory belongs
OL,17,Fto them. The Conservatives in
OL,18,Fopposition can make a difference and
OL,19,Fthis change will finally help parents
OL,20,Fand protect childhood."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FLord Nash, a Tory former education
OL,8,Fminister who led the campaign for an
OL,9,Funder-16s social media ban in the
OL,10,FHouse of Lords, said: "The Government
OL,11,Fnow has an opportunity to draw a line
OL,12,Fin the sand and end tech companies'
OL,13,Funcontrolled experiment with
OL,14,Fchildren's safety.
OL,16,F"They must deliver in full on their
OL,17,Fpledge to raise the age limit to 16
OL,18,Ffor harmful platforms and features,
OL,19,Fwith robust age verification to ensure
OL,20,Fit is properly enforced.
OL,26,@rD@WOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,F"Only by doing this can they begin to
OL,8,Fend the catastrophic harm being done
OL,9,Fto a generation. Let's give our
OL,10,Fchildren their childhood back."
OL,12,FBut some groups have argued that a ban
OL,13,Fmay not be the appropriate instrument
OL,14,Fto tackle a wide spread of social
OL,15,Fmedia harms.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FThe Molly Rose Foundation, set up in
OL,8,Fmemory of 14-year-old Molly Russell,
OL,9,Fwho took her own life in 2017 after
OL,10,Fviewing harmful content online, said a
OL,11,Fsocial media ban "will fail to tackle
OL,12,Ffundamental product safety risks
OL,13,Fissues and leaves parents with a false
OL,14,Fsense of safety".
OL,16,FChief executive Andy Burrows said: "A
OL,17,Fmajority of children will continue to
OL,18,Fuse high-risk sites that will have no
OL,19,Fincentive to implement robust
OL,20,Fprotections.
OL,26,@sD@ROUvD@PO]xD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,F"This is not what online safety
OL,8,Fexperts believe will work and is
OL,9,Fnecessary. Keir Starmer has chosen to
OL,10,Fabdicate responsibility for tackling
OL,11,Fharmful algorithms and his legacy will
OL,12,Fbe setting back children's safety by
OL,13,Fyears."
OL,15,FThe co-chairwoman of the All-Party
OL,16,FParliamentary Group for digital
OL,17,Fcreators, Labour's Feryal Clark,
OL,18,Fargued young people should not lose
OL,19,Faccess to good-quality content that
OL,20,Fhelps young people learn and find
OL,21,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FShe said: "High-quality, creator-led
OL,8,Feducational video content is a
OL,9,Fcritical public resource and is not
OL,10,Fthe same thing as social media.
OL,12,F"For example, many young people use it
OL,13,Fto revise for GCSEs, to learn a
OL,14,Flanguage or a musical instrument.
OL,16,F"Any legislative intervention must
OL,17,Fcapably address this distinction.
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,F"Failing to do so would be dangerously
OL,8,Fshort-sighted and cut off
OL,9,Fopportunities from young people at
OL,10,Fexactly the moment they need these
OL,11,Fthings most."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781481772
OL,3,CStarmer vows to end 'system failing
OL,4,Cour kids' ahead of expected social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FLeanda Barrington-Leach, executive
OL,8,Fdirector of the 5Rights Foundation, a
OL,9,Fnon-governmental organisation that
OL,10,Fcampaigns for online safety, said "a
OL,11,Fban or curfew may change who comes
OL,12,Fthrough the front door, but it does
OL,13,Fnot change what is waiting for
OL,14,Fchildren inside" and that firms must
OL,15,Fbe driven "to make their products safe
OL,16,Ffor kids".
OL,26,@rD@cOUvD@PO]wD@KOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/17
